    "en": {
      "name": "Lacrima the Scarlet Sorrow",
      "effect": "(This card is always treated as a \"Fiendsmith\" card.)\nIf this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can send 1 \"Fiendsmith\" card from your Deck to the GY, except \"Lacrima the Scarlet Sorrow\". During your opponent's turn, if this card is in your GY (Quick Effect): You can target 1 \"Fiendsmith\" Link Monster in your GY; shuffle this card into the Deck, and if you do, Special Summon that monster. You can only use each effect of \"Lacrima the Scarlet Sorrow\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
